  "title": "Customer Service Manager (Aviation/ Oil & Gas/ Pharmaceutical, up to $8,000)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Plan and execute account-level strategies that support profitability, operational efficiency, and long-term value creation.</li><li>Oversee service arrangements, ensuring commitments are met and improvement opportunities are identified and acted upon.\nExplore and develop additional opportunities within existing client relationships.</li><li>Work closely with internal stakeholders to deliver a consistent and high-quality experience to clients.</li><li>Review performance data and trends, facilitate regular business discussions, and recommend actions to improve results.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Supply Chain Management or equivalent</li><li>At least 3 years of experience managing client relationships within a commercial or operational environment in either<strong> aviation/ oil & gas / pharmaceutical industry.</strong></li><li>Capable of balancing multiple priorities and delivering outcomes within time constraints.</li></ul><p><br />If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
